{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason I went to Lwow because from correspondence with my father-- who couldn't, by the way, come back to town for the reason that before the war, he hired a German expert who was supposed to provide some improved efficiency in his manufacturing process.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, he had to fire that German expert.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't get along and so forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the war, that Germany appeared and asked my mother where my father is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was looking for my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Therefore, my father could never come back to Tarnow because he was afraid that this guy is after him, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, my father was in Lwow and he managed to get there a job in a factory, similar factory, like he had before the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was doing more or less the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had a close friend there, a Gentile, close friend, who was willing to give me housing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I knew that from letters from my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I came, I arrived at my father's factor and that the guy, who was my father's friend, agreed to let me live in his house for a while.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was like I sublet, a rental.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that point, people didn't have IDs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if I had been checked, I don't know if I would have withstood the questioning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned to avoid being-- you know, I developed a sense-- the Germans would round up Poles occasionally and catch them and send them to Germany or just interrogate them and all that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I make it my business to avoid being caught in situations like this because [? if I ?] had, it would have been very bad.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in about-- I was-- that was June.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
